{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.nodeName","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><em><code>nodeName</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n </div>\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"sect3\">\n 概述</div>\n<p>返回当前节点的节点名称</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>str</em> = <em>node</em>.nodeName;\n</pre>\n<ul>\n <li><code>str</code> 是一个存储了当前节点的节点名称的字符串。</li>\n <li><code>nodeName 是一个只读属性</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"附注","title":"附注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下表列出了所有类型的节点的<code>nodeName</code>属性的值。</p>\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>接口</th>\n   <th>nodeName 属性值</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Attr\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">Attr (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>等同于 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Attr.name\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Attr.name</a></code> 属性的值</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">CDATASection (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\"#cdata-section\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">Comment (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\"#comment\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\" title=\"DOM/document\">Document</a></td>\n   <td>\"#document\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">DocumentFragment (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\"#document-fragment\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">DocumentType (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>等同于 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/DocumentType.name\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">DocumentType.name</a></code><code> 属性的值</code></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/element\" title=\"DOM/element\">Element</a></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>等同于 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/tagName\" title=\"DOM/element.tagName\">Element.tagName</a></code> 属性的值</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Entity\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Entity</a></td>\n   <td>实体名称</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/EntityReference\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">EntityReference</a></td>\n   <td>实体引用名称</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Notation\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Notation</a></td>\n   <td>Notation 名称</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">ProcessingInstruction (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>等同于 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/ProcessingInstruction.target\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">ProcessingInstruction.target</a></code> 属性的值</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">text (en-US)</a></td>\n   <td>\"#text\"</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>假设已经存在下面的 HTML:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>d1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>hello world<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>t<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>以及下面的 JavaScript:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> div1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"d1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> text_field <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"t\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ntext_field<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> div1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>在 XHTML(以及属于 XML 类型的文档) 中，<code>变量 text_field</code>包含的值会是小写的\"div\".还在 HTML 中，<code>变量 text_field</code>包含的值会是大写的\"DIV\",<code>nodeName</code>和<code>tagName</code>属性都有这种表现。查看<a href=\"http://ejohn.org/blog/nodename-case-sensitivity/\" title=\"http://ejohn.org/blog/nodename-case-sensitivity/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">details on nodeName case sensitivity in different browsers</a>一文深入了解。</p>\n<p>如果是元素节点，<code>nodeName</code> 属性和 <code>tagName</code> 属性返回相同的值，但如果是文本节点，<code>nodeName</code>属性会返回 <code>\"#text\"</code>，而 <code>tagName</code> 属性会返回 <code>undefined</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#ref-for-dom-node-nodename①","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.Node.nodeName"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"附注","id":"附注"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"返回当前节点的节点名称","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.nodeName","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nodeName","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.nodeName","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/node/nodename","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/node/nodename/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName","title":"Node.nodeName"}],"pageTitle":"Node.nodeName - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}